-item-spacing\">Chapter Chronology</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_512\" title=\"Chapter 512\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_514\" title=\"Chapter 514\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Chapter 513</b> is titled \"Beyond Rescue!!!\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_513%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/CP9%27s_Independent_Report\" title=\"CP9&#39;s Independent Report\">CP9's Independent Report</a> Vol. 21: \"Excessive Justice\".\n</p><p><a href=\"/wiki/Rob_Lucci\" title=\"Rob Lucci\">Lucci</a> continues his assault while the Captain of the <a href=\"/wiki/Candy_Pirates\" title=\"Candy Pirates\">Candy Pirates</a> is already down. The townsfolk look on in horror at the bloodshed.&#160;\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_513%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hats</a> vanish one by one, <a href=\"/wiki/Bartholomew_Kuma\" title=\"Bartholomew Kuma\">Kuma</a> having defeated them completely.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_513%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a> wonder where <a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> disappeared to, after <a href=\"/wiki/Bartholomew_Kuma\" title=\"Bartholomew Kuma\">Kuma</a> touched him with his <a href=\"/wiki/Nikyu_Nikyu_no_Mi\" title=\"Nikyu Nikyu no Mi\">paw</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Tony_Chopper\" title=\"Tony Tony Chopper\">Chopper</a> runs wild in <a href=\"/wiki/Hito_Hito_no_Mi#Monster_Point\" title=\"Hito Hito no Mi\">Monster Point</a>, trying to hurt <a href=\"/wiki/Sentomaru\" title=\"Sentomaru\">Sentomaru</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Silvers_Rayleigh\" title=\"Silvers Rayleigh\">Rayleigh</a> is still dueling <a href=\"/wiki/Borsalino\" title=\"Borsalino\">Kizaru</a>, while <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> reflects on Kuma's ability, which she had seen at <a href=\"/wiki/Thriller_Bark\" title=\"Thriller Bark\">Thriller Bark</a> when he made <a href=\"/wiki/Perona\" title=\"Perona\">Perona</a> mysteriously vanish.\n</p><p><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> asks Sentomaru where Zoro could have gone, and Sentomaru says that anyone that gets touched by Kuma's paws would fly for three days and three nights and the destination would only be known by Kuma.\n</p><p>An outraged <a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> gets ready to battle Kuma, while <a href=\"/wiki/Pacifista\" title=\"Pacifista\">PX-1</a> tries to attack <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> from behind, using a beam attack. Kuma&#160;uses his Devil Fruit ability to send PX-1 away, enraging Sentomaru. Luffy then orders the crew to run away as far as possible. As Sanji, Usopp, and <a href=\"/wiki/Brook\" title=\"Brook\">Brook</a> try to escape, Kuma descends on them, prepared to attack. Brook sacrifices himself, making a bone joke&#160;as he disappears. Sanji is filled with despair as he begins to lose his crewmates. He tells Usopp to run and lands a kick on Kuma, only to be deflected into a pile of rubble. Usopp attempts to hold Kuma back, only to be sent away. An enraged Sanji runs at Kuma, who finally sends Sanji off as well.\n</p><p>A despaired Luffy&#160;looks on in shock. Rayleigh is still dueling Kizaru, holding off the <a href=\"/wiki/Marines\" title=\"Marines\">Marine</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Admiral\" title=\"Admiral\">Admiral</a>. Kuma then approaches Rayleigh and whispers something to him. When Kizaru asks what Kuma said to Rayleigh, Kuma simply replies with that he will not answer Kizaru's questions.\n</p><p>Luffy activates <a href=\"/wiki/Gomu_Gomu_no_Mi/Gear_2_Techniques\" title=\"Gomu Gomu no Mi/Gear 2 Techniques\">Gear 2</a> as Kuma teleports to where <a href=\"/wiki/Franky\" title=\"Franky\">Franky</a> and Nami are. Franky tries to attack Kuma with a <a href=\"/wiki/Battle_Frankies/BF-36\" title=\"Battle Frankies/BF-36\">\"Strong Right\"</a>, but it has no effect. An enraged Luffy tries a \"Jet Pistol\", only to be blocked by Kuma's paws. Kuma descends on Franky and sends him away using his Devil Fruit ability. Luffy slowly succumbs to defeat, as Nami is also sent away by Kuma.\n</p><p>With only <a href=\"/wiki/Nico_Robin\" title=\"Nico Robin\">Robin</a> and a Monster Chopper left, Luffy desperately lunges at Kuma. However, Kuma simply teleports again, to Robin and Chopper. Luffy starts begging Kuma to stop sending his crewmates away but Kuma still sends Chopper away. Robin attempts to run; however, she also gets sent away by Kuma.\n</p><p>Luffy, filled with despair and rage, falls to the ground, angry and crying&#160;that he could not even save a single friend. Kuma simply responds by saying that he will not be seeing Luffy again and ultimately sends Luffy flying, resulting in the utter defeat of the Straw Hats.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_513%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_513%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Bartholomew_Kuma\" title=\"Bartholomew Kuma\">Kuma</a> makes <a href=\"/wiki/Pacifista\" title=\"Pacifista\">PX-1</a> \"<a href=\"/wiki/Nikyu_Nikyu_no_Mi\" title=\"Nikyu Nikyu no Mi\">vanish</a>\".</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sentomaru\" title=\"Sentomaru\">Sentomaru</a> explains that whenever Kuma makes someone \"vanish\", he actually sends them flying far away for three days and three nights to another destination.</li>\n<li>Kuma whispers something to <a href=\"/wiki/Silvers_Rayleigh\" title=\"Silvers Rayleigh\">Silvers Rayleigh</a>.</li>\n<li>The Straw Hat Pirates are utterly \"eradicated\" by Kuma.</li>\n<li>This is the last chapter of the <a href=\"/wiki/Sabaody_Archipelago_Arc\" title=\"Sabaody Archipelago Arc\">Sabaody Archipelago Arc</a>.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_513%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Marines\" title=\"Marines\">Marines</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/World_Government\" title=\"World Government\">World Government</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Tony_Tony_Chopper\" title=\"Tony Tony Chopper\">Tony Tony Chopper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nico_Robin\" title=\"Nico Robin\">Nico Robin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Franky\" title=\"Franky\">Franky</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Brook\" title=\"Brook\">Brook</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Seven_Warlords_of_the_Sea\" title=\"Seven Warlords of the Sea\">Seven Warlords of the Sea</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Bartholomew_Kuma\" title=\"Bartholomew Kuma\">Bartholomew Kuma</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Candy_Pirates\" title=\"Candy Pirates\">Candy Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Candy\" title=\"Candy\">Candy</a> <i>(cover)</i></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Admiral\" title=\"Admiral\">Admiral</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Borsalino\" title=\"Borsalino\">Kizaru</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Sentomaru\" title=\"Sentomaru\">Sentomaru</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Pacifista\" title=\"Pacifista\">PX-1</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/CP9\" title=\"CP9\">CP9</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Rob_Lucci\" title=\"Rob Lucci\">Rob Lucci</a> <i>(cover)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hattori\" title=\"Hattori\">Hattori</a> <i>(cover)</i></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Sabaody_Archipelago\" title=\"Sabaody Archipelago\">Sabaody Archipelago</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Silvers_Rayleigh\" title=\"Silvers Rayleigh\">Silvers Rayleigh</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_513%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nThe Shinobu Kaitani Pirate Crew attacked our office. What a nuisance. Come back anytime.</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\n海賊甲斐谷忍一味が仕事場に来襲。も～うるっさいうるさい。また来て下さい。</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_513%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<p><b>← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_512\" title=\"Chapter 512\">Previous Chapter</a></b>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:right;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_514\" title=\"Chapter 514\">Next Chapter</a> →</b>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; font-size:90%; clear:both; text-align:center; width:80%;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"cs SummitWarSagaColors\" style=\"\" colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/wiki/Sabaody_Archipelago_Arc\" title=\"Sabaody Archipelago Arc\">Sabaody Archipelago Arc</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"cs SummitWarSagaColors\" style=\"\" colspan=\"12\"><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Sabaody_Archipelago_Arc_Chapters\" title=\"Category:Sabaody Archipelago Arc Chapters\">Manga Chapters</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_490\" title=\"Chapter 490\">490</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_491\" title=\"Chapter 491\">491</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_492\" title=\"Chapter 492\">492</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_493\" title=\"Chapter 493\">493</a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-ali